  "title": "Analyst (Laboratory)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare routine solutions and reagents and perform standard laboratory reactions</li><li>Make, observe, and accurately record experimental observations</li><li>Perform basic calculations and data analysis</li><li>Collect and prepare data for evaluation and reporting</li><li>Support laboratory operations by stocking and distributing supplies and equipment</li><li>Set up and dismantle laboratory apparatus as required</li><li>Collect, wash, and store glassware following laboratory procedures</li><li>Perform technical tasks and maintain records in compliance with company and regulatory standards</li><li>Ensure quality, accuracy, and data integrity in all laboratory activities</li><li>Analyzing compounds and manage corporate compound collections</li><li>Perform technical procedures across Production, R&D, Quality Control/Assurance, and Compliance/Environmental areas</li></ul><p></p>",
